creator: Subsplash Inc
descriptionHtml:
Welcome to the official Catalyst Church app!

At Catalyst Church we aim to be a unique church provoking lasting change by sharing compassion and hope. We hope that in this church you will find people who are welcoming and a place where relationships are a big deal. A place where you can know God more and worship Him freely. A place where you are welcome to learn and grow at your own pace and ask questions along the way. A place where you can be yourself and find friends. But most importantly, a place where you feel at home and you can connect with Jesus Christ in a real way.

Here are some great features of the app that we think you'll love:
- receive push notifications from the church
- stay up to date with events coming up
- read the bible with the in built Bible reader
- give online from the convenience of your mobile phone
- Access daily scriptures to read along with our daily bible reading plan
- Download messages right to your device to listen offline
- Social network sharing on all platforms

For more information about Catalyst Church please visit: http://www.catalystchurch.com.au
We are located at 142 Pine Mountain Road, Brassall, Queensland, Australia.
